com.google.api.client.googleapis.notifications

Class AbstractNotification

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.api.client.googleapis.notifications.AbstractNotification
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    TypedNotification, UnparsedNotification

    @Beta
public abstract class AbstractNotification
extends Object
    Beta
    Notification metadata sent to this client about a watched resource.

    Implementation is not thread-safe.

    Since:
    1.16
    Author:
    Yaniv Inbar, Matthias Linder (mlinder)
